    bibo:volume "5403" ;
    dc:creator "Fleck, Günther" ;
    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "A remarkable new synthemistid from New Caledonia (Odonata: Anisoptera: Synthemistidae s. str.). Taxonomic and phylogenetic note on New Caledonian Synthemistidae and erection of a new genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561958>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561950> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561958>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–24. 22. Comparison of paratype female Calesynthemis jeanlegrandi sp. nov. (left) and female Calesynthemis serendipita (right). 23. Neocaledosynthemis gen. nov. N. fenella. Vesica spermalis (or penis) in right lateral view.Arrow indicates common stem of dh1 and dh2. 24. Synthemis tasmanica. Vesica spermalis (or penis). V3 and V4 in right lateral view. Note the remarkable similarity with V3 and V4 of Neocaledosynthemis fenella gen. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561958/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561950>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–10. Calesynthemis jeanlegrandi sp. nov., male holotype. Vesica spermalis (or penis). 6. Left general view. 7. Ventral general view. 8. Detail of V2–V4 in right lateral view. 9. Detail of V3 in ventral view. 10. Detail of V3–V4 in anteroventral view. Note the strongly divergent branches of dh1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561950/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

